        "children": []
      },
      {
        "element": "span",
        "class": "",
        "text": "] Both the order to dig trenches, and the promise of water are prefaced in this solemn manner. It is no order of his own which the prophet delivers.",
        "children": []
      },
      {
        "element": "span",
        "class": "p",
